subject: we're still missing your reponse!
body: Sorry to bump you on this, friend, but our deadline is just 14 hours away — and we're still missing your response! And right now, Vice President Kamala Harris and Donald Trump are still NECK AND NECK in the polls. At Team Gillibrand, our strategy is driven by on-the-ground, real-time input from folks like you. And with so much at stake, and early voting already underway for many, it's essential that we know where our supporters stand.
